e when="1992">1992</date></imprint><biblScope unit="pp">50–51</biblScope></monogr></biblStruct></listBibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><langUsage><language ident="de-AT">German</language></langUsage><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName><date when="1893-08-11" n="01">11. 8. 1893</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</persName><placeName ref="#pmb213">Bad Ischl</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1893-08-03_01">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 3. 8. 1893</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1893-08-18_01">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 18. 8. 1893</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
